## Limitations

The information gathered is based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of fair trade practices globally. The data is primarily from organizations and articles that support fair trade, which may introduce a bias towards positive outcomes. Additionally, the effectiveness and impact of fair trade can vary significantly across different regions and products, which may not be fully captured in this report.